data.description: Great location in Celina Schools. Located in the quiet country town of Weston. If you are looking for a house to remodel or a lot to build on this is the one for you. This lot is located close to major cities and roads, but you still get the country feeling. You will not be able to beat living in Weston. Just down the street from Downtown, hard to find lots in this part of the country that have the potential of this one.
